{"tid":1471301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲遊客明白及體諒示威者行為","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:54:31.000Z","uid":249480,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1040935e58be8cbf787a964fa03e52c4557670","tid":1471301,"uid":249480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14jibN1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14jibN1.png&h=bae3ed52&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dh0AYs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDh0AYs4.png&h=aa813221&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大致上話佢明白大部分琴日既人都係和平集會，雖然有阻佢入禁區但係問左學生如果佢真係要入會唔會阻，學生話唔會。最後仲話係榮幸可以面對面見到學生。<br />\n<br />\n記住我地唔係暴徒，和理非，有禮貌就得<br />\n好多人企我地呢邊，唔好比仇恨支配自己<br />\n818我要見到晒你地<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n勿忘初衷"},{"pid":"3bd2ba6560ba53834998caf8a471375e62e6a308","tid":1471301,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YvdK1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YvdK1E.jpg&h=e1c38679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D83Sf8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD83Sf8j.jpg&h=da01072f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSeBHOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSeBHOk.jpg&h=4d624e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7KeuxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7KeuxB.jpg&h=6eb7f2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na